1586
01:21:31.597 --> 01:21:33.722
No! No!

1587
01:21:33.722 --> 01:21:36.639
Spielberg:
Nothing could prepare me for
my first visit to Auschwitz.


1588
01:21:36.639 --> 01:21:38.222
Nothing prepared me
