( chattering )

2392
02:00:58.263 --> 02:00:59.889
Todd McCarthy:
From about the time


2393
02:00:59.889 --> 02:01:01.931
of the millennium
in Spielberg's career,


2394
02:01:01.931 --> 02:01:06.347
there is something,
whether it's personal,
political, historical,


2395
02:01:06.347 --> 02:01:10.388
that pushed him
in a more adventurous
and a darker direction.


2396
02:01:10.388 --> 02:01:12.181
I fundamentally
don't buy


2397
02:01:12.181 --> 02:01:14.764
that he has
a pessimistic worldview


2398
02:01:14.764 --> 02:01:19.181
or that he suddenly changed
and has a more dubious opinion


2399
02:01:19.181 --> 02:01:21.931
of the human race,
but still,


2400
02:01:21.931 --> 02:01:24.805
there's been
an alteration.


2401
02:01:24.805 --> 02:01:27.305
He has been willing
to go places


2402
02:01:27.305 --> 02:01:30.430
that he would not have gone
in his earlier films.


2403
02:01:31.472 --> 02:01:33.847
( chatter on TV )

2404
02:01:35.430 --> 02:01:37.680
All right, Howard Marks.
Where are you?


2405
02:01:37.680 --> 02:01:40.139
It was a very complicated
story, "Minority Report."


2406
02:01:40.139 --> 02:01:41.764
A very dark story,
actually.


2407
02:01:41.764 --> 02:01:44.305
You know, democracy,
freedom of choice,


2408
02:01:44.305 --> 02:01:46.722
corruption.

2409
02:01:46.722 --> 02:01:49.097
Spielberg:
That dark, futuristic
dystopian tone


2410
02:01:49.097 --> 02:01:51.513
was so compelling for me
at that time.


2411
02:01:51.513 --> 02:01:53.472
Kushner:
Tennessee Williams
says that artists


2412
02:01:53.472 --> 02:01:55.680
are like the canaries
in the coal mine.


2413
02:01:55.680 --> 02:01:58.222
And Steven has
an uncanny knack


2414
02:01:58.222 --> 02:02:02.263
for feeling what's going on
in the world around him


2415
02:02:02.263 --> 02:02:05.764
and what needs to be said
at its moment.


2416
02:02:05.764 --> 02:02:09.014
I think he's
a very present filmmaker.


2417
02:02:09.014 --> 02:02:11.388
By mandate
of the District of Columbia
Precrime Division,


2418
02:02:11.388 --> 02:02:14.847
I'm placing you under
