2419
02:02:14.847 --> 02:02:18.388
Hoberman:
The film anticipated
the whole post-9/11 mentality


2420
02:02:18.388 --> 02:02:21.388
of arresting people
before they can commit crimes


2421
02:02:21.388 --> 02:02:23.014
and preventive detention
and so on.


2422
02:02:27.097 --> 02:02:28.639
Spielberg:
But the movie that I made


2423
02:02:28.639 --> 02:02:31.847
that was a real statement
about 9/11


2424
02:02:31.847 --> 02:02:33.181
was "War of the Worlds."

2425
02:02:33.181 --> 02:02:35.139
( people screaming )

2426
02:02:37.181 --> 02:02:40.889
Spielberg:
For me, it began with
what would really happen


2427
02:02:40.889 --> 02:02:42.805
if we were invaded

2428
02:02:42.805 --> 02:02:44.722
and everything
that we thought


2429
02:02:44.722 --> 02:02:47.889
made us invulnerable
to invasion


2430
02:02:47.889 --> 02:02:48.972
was all wrong?

2431
02:02:51.222 --> 02:02:53.097
( people screaming )

2432
02:03:00.639 --> 02:03:02.764
Koepp:
There's a sequence
where Cruise's character


2433
02:03:02.764 --> 02:03:05.764
runs through the streets
and the ray is turning
people to dust


2434
02:03:05.764 --> 02:03:09.097
and some of that dust
is in his hair.


2435
02:03:09.097 --> 02:03:11.263
And he comes home
and sees himself in shock


2436
02:03:11.263 --> 02:03:14.805
and realizes
that that's remains
that are in his hair.


2437
02:03:14.805 --> 02:03:16.513
- Oh!
- ( water running )


2438
02:03:16.513 --> 02:03:19.222
Koepp:
Steven handled that
with great tact.


2439
02:03:19.222 --> 02:03:22.014
9/11 was so much a part
of our national psyche,


2440
02:03:22.014 --> 02:03:25.263
you didn't have to do much
to evoke the shock we all felt


2441
02:03:25.263 --> 02:03:28.181
and the helplessness
we all felt at being attacked.


2442
02:03:31.680 --> 02:03:34.305
( all shouting )

2443
02:03:37.305 --> 02:03:40.056
( shouting continues )

2444
02:03:43.722 --> 02:03:45.597
( screaming )

2445
02:03:45.597 --> 02:03:49.597
( shouting continues )

2446
02:03:49.597 --> 02:03:51.722
Good afternoon.
I'm Jim McKay speaking to you


2447
02:03:51.722 --> 02:03:54.847
live at this moment
from ABC headquarters


2448
02:03:54.847 --> 02:03:58.181
just outside the Olympic Village
in Munich, West Germany.


2449
02:03:58.181 --> 02:04:01.263
The peace of what is--
would've been called
the "Serene Olympics"


2450
02:04:01.263 --> 02:04:04.889
was shattered just before dawn
