2453
02:04:10.764 --> 02:04:12.513
to weigh in
on the Middle East


2454
02:04:12.513 --> 02:04:14.347
because
it's such a minefield,


2455
02:04:14.347 --> 02:04:16.472
and Steven
is not a sensationalist


2456
02:04:16.472 --> 02:04:19.805
in the sense
of wanting to create,


2457
02:04:19.805 --> 02:04:22.555
you know, firestorms
of controversy.


2458
02:04:22.555 --> 02:04:25.014
- Jim: This is
building number 31.
- ( chatter )


2459
02:04:25.014 --> 02:04:26.764
At this moment,

2460
02:04:26.764 --> 02:04:29.972
eight or nine terrified
living human beings


2461
02:04:29.972 --> 02:04:31.847
- are being held prisoner.
