2462
02:04:31.847 --> 02:04:35.097
Spielberg:
I felt I could not
make this one-sided.


2463
02:04:35.097 --> 02:04:39.555
And so, I knew
it would be controversial
from the very get-go.


2464
02:04:39.555 --> 02:04:42.472
( woman vocalizing )

2465
02:04:51.764 --> 02:04:53.805
- ( chatter on TV )
- ( overlapping voices )


2466
02:04:56.181 --> 02:04:59.388
Eric Bana:
It was that story
of the group of Mossad agents


2467
02:04:59.388 --> 02:05:01.931
who were assembled
to avenge the deaths


2468
02:05:01.931 --> 02:05:04.972
of the Israeli athletes
at the Munich Olympics.


2469
02:05:09.097 --> 02:05:13.305
It was their job
to go after a list
of targeted men


2470
02:05:13.305 --> 02:05:16.472
who were part
of a terrorist group.


2471
02:05:16.472 --> 02:05:20.430
And it was
their job to, one by one,
assassinate them.


2472
02:05:20.430 --> 02:05:23.931
Daniel Craig:
This movie was trying to affect
and turn on a debate.


2473
02:05:23.931 --> 02:05:27.014
Is vengeance the answer?
