solve anything?


2474
02:05:27.014 --> 02:05:29.014
If you continue
the cycle of violence


2475
02:05:29.014 --> 02:05:30.847
and cycle of blood,
then...


2476
02:05:30.847 --> 02:05:33.847
that's what they'll be
and nothing else.


2477
02:05:36.014 --> 02:05:38.639
Steven was very keen
to tell a human story,


2478
02:05:38.639 --> 02:05:42.305
that these were men
and not superheroes.


2479
02:05:42.305 --> 02:05:45.513
Their indecision
and their mistakes


2480
02:05:45.513 --> 02:05:49.014
and their-- is the reality
of what happened, you know?


2481
02:05:49.014 --> 02:05:51.722
Life isn't
a "James Bond" movie.
( chuckles )


2482
02:05:51.722 --> 02:05:53.347
Are you--
are you Wael Zwaiter?


2483
02:05:53.347 --> 02:05:55.597
He said yes already.
